Text:
ESET NOD32 detected 
Win32/Chepdu.AC virus in the main setup file and not in the crack.  

Read description about this virus at http://www.eset.eu/encyclopaedia/win32-chepdu-ac-trojan-downloader-banload-atdp-p-pws-banker-fss?lng=en

It could be a fake alarm but never observed fake alarm for the main setup file. It is generally common with cracks, patches and keygen. 



(Aliases:    Trojan-Downloader.Win32.Banload.atdp (Kaspersky), Trojan:Win32/Chepdu.P (Microsoft), PWS-Banker!fss trojan (McAfee) 
Type of infiltration:    Trojan  
Size:    241664 B 
Affected platforms:    Microsoft Windows 
Signature database version:    4988 (20100331)
